jobInfo.postDescription:
Requirement: 
1. Major in Computer Science or equivalent qualification.
2. With 2+ years experience in Java/JEE.
3. Have a good command of JEE technologies, including Spring, JSF, Spring WebFlow, Hibernate, JPA and etc, as well as popular design patterns.
4. Proficient with oracle or SQL Server.
5. CET-4 or above, good command of speaking and writing English.
6. Experienced in code review and tuning.
7. Possess interest programming and desire to be expert in java technology domain.
8. Experience in Insurance project is a plus.
9. Experience in maven is a plus.
10. Experience in Scrum is a plus.
Job Description:
1. Provide programming expertise in delivery of projects. 
2. Key responsibilities may include analyze specifications and translate it to code;
3. Manage changes to configurable items (hardware, software, documentation etc).
4. Develop unit test package, execute test & document test result to ensure quality of program.
5. Assist in integration test, UAT & implementation activities; assist in preparation of user manual & training materials.
6. Investigate all reported problems/errors & initiate amendments & testing.
7. Prepare & maintain up-to-date system documentation.

brandComInfo.introduce:
EIS总部位于美国旧金山，在欧洲和美国其他城市拥有13家全资子公司。全球员工总数超过两千余人，公司通过了CMMI5和ISO9001 2000认证。 
EIS是世界领先的保险应用软件供应商，致力于为全球财、寿险公司提供保险核心业务应用软件解决方案。EIS与全球众多知名保险公司都建立了长久的合作，客户遍及全球五大洲20多个国家及地区, 如ACE, CHARTIS, AMI等。公司2000余名员工来自全球不同国家，专注于保险业务运营咨询、产品管理或项目实施、软件研发等专业领域。 
EIS完善而严格的管理制度，跨国际事业的理念还有语言上的优势造就了现在的成功。我们的使命是利用先进的软件技术，结合自身深厚的行业知识和实施经验，为社会各界提供先进的协同应用系统、解决方案及其他服务。
